    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Mountain Retreat you build, furnish and decorate Lodges in the mountains and advertise for lodgers to stay throughout the year. Keep them happy by feeding them delicious meals cooked using ingredients from your farm. Tend to your farm throughout the year for a wide variety of meals to serve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off Wolves, Bears and Bats in the Delves - dungeons underground in engaging combat (<u><strong>optional - can be turned off</strong></u>) using a variety of crafted, non-breakable weaponry.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/9255517382b8b20bdbe46c86eaeb6120.avif?t=1772124070\" width=864 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/ab62c7dc55c368232c3cba6b31227111.webp?t=1772124070\" width=800 height=62 /></span>Fell trees for wood, mine for ore, craft and smelt to build and decorate cosy cabins and relaxing glamping pods by the lake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/b3d8aeff9cb989d6399d116065d1a78b.poster.avif?t=1772124070\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/b3d8aeff9cb989d6399d116065d1a78b.webm?t=1772124070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/b3d8aeff9cb989d6399d116065d1a78b.mp4?t=1772124070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/c9fbe288984b00390435610101819996.avif?t=1772124070\" width=224 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/415bf9c580648a527812acf41a124bf9.webp?t=1772124070\" width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultivate and harvest fresh ingredients from your farm to cook meals for your guests who stay at your Retreat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/f30b37c91c28965f022b5c5a8466c1e2.poster.avif?t=1772124070\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/f30b37c91c28965f022b5c5a8466c1e2.webm?t=1772124070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/f30b37c91c28965f022b5c5a8466c1e2.mp4?t=1772124070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: right\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/17c3569944464c5a23dd9d893d345856.webp?t=1772124070\" width=128 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/4d22475bc2e70eff99346080d9883ea4.webp?t=1772124070\" width=800 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transfer holiday makers to their dream refuge to spend a week in the beautiful glades of the lake and oversee their happiness providing an unforgettable and pleasant stay. <br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/e6866543548c3320db9b7683618b92ba.poster.avif?t=1772124070\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/e6866543548c3320db9b7683618b92ba.webm?t=1772124070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/e6866543548c3320db9b7683618b92ba.mp4?t=1772124070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take them on speedboat water-ski adventures on the great Springblue Lagoon and cook them fabulous meals at Capstone Hall - homegrown ingredients from your Farm of course! There's plenty to see and do in Mountain Retreat. Enjoy your stay! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160420/extras/785575861866269d11ccb953ff22f9b1.avif?t=1772124070\" width=240 height=64 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong> </strong></i></u>Till, Plant, Water flowers and harvest crops.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chop trees and collect wood for building and crafting.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use horse and cart for transporting materials and Lodgers to their lodge.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish a wide variety of fish. Bake fresh bread from your harvested wheat and mill-ground flour. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build Lodges and advertise and rent-out to Lodgers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mine ores and smelt weaponry.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off any wolves and other enemy types. Combat is <strong>optional (can be turned off per new game).</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your lodges with furniture pre-bought and crafted. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook for lodgers from a variety of recipes. Either to orders or just hand out wherever you go.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lodgers will rate their stay and leave messages and star ratings in the Town hall guestbook. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests from the games characters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lodgers participate in holiday activities such as fishing, exploring the mountains, hosting BBQ's and Water skiing. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Canoes and speedboats help you get around quickly or take a Skycar up into the mountains. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Autosave enabled (configurable) - no need to sleep and rest-up energy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon woodland creatures to help you cut trees, harvest crops and fast travel across the world map.</p></li></ul>",
